'''Matthew Hatton''' is an artist who illustrated many of the ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Wizards of the Coast]] sourcebooks. Hatton made [[Wikipedia:Illustration|illustrations]] for the ''[[Endor and the Moddell Sector]]'' article in [[Star Wars Gamer 9|''Star Wars Gamer'' 9]]. He also provided [[Wikipedia:Storyboard|storyboard]] illustrations and [[Wikipedia:Concept art|concept art]] for the film [[Wikipedia:2006|2006]] film [[Wikipedia:Happy Feet|''Happy Feet'']].

